    SearchPhenotypeAssociationSetsResponse:
      description: This is the response from `POST /phenotypeassociationsets/search` expressed as JSON.

          description: |-

            Provide this value in a subsequent request to return the next page of

          type: string

          items:

          type: array
      type: object
